milestones.description: Iain Butchart has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran
Syed Kirmani has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (5) in ODIs for IND, going past Syed Kirmani's 3
Fletcher and Dave Houghton's 35-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Fletcher and Andy Pycroft
